Introduction

Young Bin is a South Korean singer-songwriter and rapper under FNC Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group SF9. Youngbin is considered the Dad of the group, often seen taking good care of maknae Chani. As a 1MILLION dance studio trainee, Youngbin's passion for performing led him to train and eventually debut.

He debuted as the leader of SF9 on October 5, 2016, with the group's first single album "Feeling Sensation".

He acted in the drama “I Need Romance Season 3” (2014, Ep. 8, 11). “Click Your Heart” (2016) “Was it Love?” (2020, Ep. 6), “Bubble Up” (2022). Youngbin has 2 tattoos. One goes down his left side and says “Shine Forever.” The other is by his collarbone and says “sic parvis magna.”
